.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, ambient, punk, dubstep
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, volleyball, tennis, cricket
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
4. the fan of dubstep is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
5. the fan of reggae is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | ambient         | dubstep   | reggae    |
| Sport         | volleyball | cricket | tennis | skateboarding |

