.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, sports, musical, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, parkour, cricket, skiing
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching sports movies##7
2. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person watching musical movies and the person watching thriller movies##7
4. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
5. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere between the person watching sports movies and the person who's sport is parkour##7
6. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
7. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the person watching thriller movies##8
8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports   | musical | martial-arts | thriller    |
| Sport         | tennis | skiing   | cricket   | parkour |

