.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, grapes, cabbage, lime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, jazz, r&b, country
1. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the person eating radish##5
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
4. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
5. the person eating radish is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5
6. the person eating lime is not to the left of the fan of jazz##8
7. the person eating lime is the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | lime | radish | grapes  | cabbage |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | country         | r&b | blues |

