.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, soy-milk, milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, surfing, snowboarding, swimming
1. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the person drinking juice##8
2. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person who's sport is snowboarding##7
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5
4. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8
5. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person drinking juice##8
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | juice      | soy-milk | coffee | milk   |
| Sport      | tennis | snowboarding | swimming  | surfing |

