3. the teacher is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the teacher##7
5. the pilot is not to the right of the designer##8
6. the designer is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the pilot##7

.:: Answer ::.
