.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, country, gospel, r&b
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, train, helicopter, skateboard
1. the fan of reggae is between the fan of r&b and the person driving the quad-bike##2
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
4. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
5. the person driving the train is the person driving the train##1
6. the fan of gospel is not the person driving the helicopter##6
7. the fan of r&b is not to the right of the fan of gospel##8
8. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the left of the person driving the train##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | reggae | gospel | country |
| Transport     | skateboard | train       | quad-bike  | helicopter    |

