.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, grapes, cherry, blueberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, fishing, rock-climbing, video-games
1. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the right of the person eating grapes##8
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person eating blueberry##5
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating cherry is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
6. the person eating grapes is on the far left##1
7. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | grapes        | blueberry | cherry      | peas    |
| Hobby   | gardening | rock-climbing   | fishing | video-games |

