.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, water, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, basketball, rowing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person who's sport is rowing and the person drinking coffee##7
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | coffee         | water    | lemonade       |
| Sport      | basketball | weightlifting | tennis | rowing |

