 1. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
 2. the person eating asparagus is not to the left of the person eating lime##8
 3. the person eating cranberry is the person watching documentary movies##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is not to the right of the person watching mystery movies##8
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating lime##5
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating cranberry is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8
 9. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person eating cranberry##8
10. the person eating cherry is not to the left of the person watching epic movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | cherry    | lime | cranberry | asparagus |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | musical  | documentary     | mystery    |

