.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, onion, garlic, artichoke
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, chess, sudoku, singing
1. the person eating garlic is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person eating garlic is not to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##8
3. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person eating artichoke##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating onion##1
6. the person eating onion is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person eating artichoke##2
7. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | artichoke        | onion | banana | garlic |
| Hobby   | singing | sudoku | chess   | magic-tricks    |

