.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, horse, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, motorbike, tram
1. the owner of the turtle is not the person driving the motorbike##6
2. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8
3. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the owner of the turtle##7
4. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
5. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
6. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the right of the person driving the bus##8
7. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | hamster  | turtle | bird  | horse  |
| Transport   | quad-bike | bus   | tram | motorbike |

