.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, cat, goat, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, scooter, tram, bus
1. the person driving the scooter is not the owner of the pony##6
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
4. the owner of the goat is the person driving the bike##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the bike##7
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
7. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the bus and the owner of the goat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | cat    | guinea-pig | pony | goat |
| Transport   | scooter | bus      | tram     | bike     |

 